Response: User age distribution squished below 30. Surprising spike at 100+ not fully explained by January month (default value) -> might be confusion about year 00 : i.e. 1900 or 2000… spike of users with 1905 birth year might be users born in 2005 with mistaken entry (facebook allow 11 year olds?) ***

Getting Logical

summary(pf$mobile_likes)
##    Min. 1st Qu.  Median    Mean 3rd Qu.    Max.
